    <item>
      <title>15｜同位语的两个重要作用</title>
      <link>https://politcloud.org/post/%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/%E4%BA%92%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E7%A7%81%E6%95%99%E8%AF%BE/15%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%8D%E8%AF%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://politcloud.org/post/%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/%E4%BA%92%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E7%A7%81%E6%95%99%E8%AF%BE/15%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%8D%E8%AF%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;你好，我是陈亦峰，欢迎你和我一起学英语。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;今天我们继续阅读Successful Remote Working 这篇文章。我带你深入分析句子、讲解词汇。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;课前朗读&#34;&gt;课前朗读&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The first starting point for remote employees is to have clear separation between home and work. This can be done through physical separation, by having a dedicated home office, or even working at a shared-work facility, such as Regus or WeWork. It is also helpful to have a transition point, something to replace a commute, that delineates the shift from being at home to being at work. Some people have found taking their dog for a walk, or simply going out the front door and coming in the back door of their house is enough to make the mental shift and start focusing on work.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>16｜动词：英语宇宙的中心</title>
      <link>https://politcloud.org/post/%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/%E4%BA%92%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E7%A7%81%E6%95%99%E8%AF%BE/16%E5%8A%A8%E8%AF%8D%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E5%AE%87%E5%AE%99%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/</link>
